    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "事務所に届いていたファンレターを持って来たんです\n……って、なんですか、その格好は！　ハレンチな！",
      "startTime": 15.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.9780272961
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "誰がハレンチよ！　これはクリスマスイベントで\n着る衣装よ。変なこと言わないでちょうだい",
      "startTime": 22.6646939437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "それに、今日はたまたま試着していただけで\n普段からこんな格好してる訳じゃないから",
      "startTime": 29.4646939437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.2813604197
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません。でも俺の記憶だと、衣装のデザインは\nこんなに露出が多くなかったはずですが……",
      "startTime": 36.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "ララ達のイベント出演が決まって\n彼女達の衣装も追加で作ることになったでしょ？",
      "startTime": 43.0485488098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.8052141669
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "でも急な話で材料は増やせないから、限られた材料で\n追加分の衣装も作れるようにアレンジしたの",
      "startTime": 51.4818808716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "その結果、元のデザインよりも\n一人分の布面積がかなり少なくなったのよ",
      "startTime": 57.3152142049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.8121304991
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
